            <span class="ml-3 text-gray-700">Priority email support</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <div class="mt-8">
          <%= link_to "Upgrade Course", license_status_path,
              class: "block w-full rounded-lg bg-blue-600 py-3 px-4 text-center text-sm font-medium text-white hover:bg-blue-700" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <div class="mt-20">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-12">
        Frequently Asked Questions
      </h2>

      <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
            Who pays for the upgrade?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            The instructor pays for course upgrades. This keeps things simple and gives instructors direct control over their course capacity.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
            What happens at the end of the semester?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Course access expires at the end of the semester. You can archive your course data and renew for the next semester if needed.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
            Can I try before upgrading?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Absolutely! Start with the free tier (3 students) to test the platform. Upgrade only when you need more students.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
            Do you offer institutional pricing?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            We're focused on individual instructor needs for now. Institutional pricing may be available in the future.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
            What payment methods do you accept?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            We accept all major credit cards and debit cards through our secure payment processor.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
            Can I get a refund?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Yes, we offer a 30-day money-back guarantee if you're not satisfied with the platform.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Contact Section -->
    <div class="mt-20 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        Have questions about pricing?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
        We're here to help you choose the right plan for your needs.
      </p>
      <a href="mailto:support@bizlaw.edu?subject=Pricing Question"
         class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-lg text-white bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700">
        Contact Support
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
